## 4. 데이터 모델 — 신규 테이블

### `TB_TRM_CUSTOM_WORD`

```sql
-- db-ddl/06_custom_word.sql
CREATE TABLE TB_TRM_CUSTOM_WORD (
    CUSTOM_WORD_SN   NUMBER          NOT NULL,
    WORD_KR_NM       VARCHAR2(200)   NOT NULL,
    WORD_ENG_NM      VARCHAR2(200),
    WORD_ENG_ABBR_NM VARCHAR2(50),
    REASON_CN        VARCHAR2(500),
    USE_YN           CHAR(1)         DEFAULT 'Y' NOT NULL,
    RGTR_ID          VARCHAR2(20),
    REG_DT           TIMESTAMP,
    MDFR_ID          VARCHAR2(20),
    MDFCN_DT         TIMESTAMP,
    CONSTRAINT PK_TB_TRM_CUSTOM_WORD PRIMARY KEY (CUSTOM_WORD_SN)
);
CREATE SEQUENCE TB_TRM_CUSTOM_WORD_SEQ START WITH 1 INCREMENT BY 1;

INSERT INTO TB_TRM_SCHEMA_HISTORY (FILE_NM) VALUES ('06_custom_word.sql');
COMMIT;
```

### Java 레이어

| 파일 | 역할 |
|---|---|
| `entity/CustomWord.java` | JPA Entity, `@SequenceGenerator` |
| `repository/CustomWordRepository.java` | `JpaRepository<CustomWord, Long>` |
| `service/CustomWordService.java` | 검색/저장 로직 |
| `vo/CustomWordVo.java` | MCP 응답 전용 |

